  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is an observational, physiology pilot study of subjects with overactive bladder,
      insomnia and normal subjects. No study drug will be given. All subjects will complete a one
      week sleep diary and a 3-day bladder diary. After one week, subjects meeting eligibility
      requirements will complete a single sleep night stay in a sleep laboratory setting. During
      the sleep night stay, subjects will be evaluated using cystometry and polysomnography. In the
      morning following the sleep night stay, subjects will complete a sleep questionnaire and this
      will complete their participation in the study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
